Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们久等了的薪酬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的  小波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一…一万円
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我汗水与泪水的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,该用来买什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,新的乐谱?  全套漫画收藏?
